{"tid":949030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英駐港總領館派操粵語官員　探望泰國菲律賓等服刑持 BNO 港人","createTime":"2018-12-20T13:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T06:19:46.000Z","uid":5195,"like":356,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a4543beceda1a1fa5b8ecbfbfec7ffb06cd19849","tid":949030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"英國駐港總領事館今天在其官方 facebook 專頁「UK in Hong Kong 」的專頁發帖，指英國駐香港總領事館領事部人員，近日探訪在泰國、印尼、菲律賓及台灣的英國國民（海外）在囚人士。照片所見，領事人員分別到過位於泰國曼谷的孔普雷中央監獄（Klong Prem Central Prison）以及菲律賓懲教局的 New Bilibid Prison。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港總領事館又提到，操粵語官員可協助向在囚人士，傳遞香港家庭成員的訊息，並分發當地華文雜誌。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府的網頁報道指，持有在英國國民（海外）護照（即 BNO），有權在香港、澳門、中國大陸和英國境外旅行時，獲得英國政府的領事服務。他們可以向全球 228 個英國代表團申請領事服務，服務包括幫助更換丟失、被盜、損壞或過期的護照；在意外、住院、死亡和犯罪受害者提供緊急援助，另外還有 遣返、資金轉移和公證服務。"},{"pid":"142858ad246d7b2d276d57e2f11789af2598be29","tid":949030,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c016e7238df122ca594fc6558068aa5bfda95ca2","tid":949030,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8bc1c4df6dfee22d66be9d9773acda107b91f5","tid":949030,"uid":9338,"like":162,"dislike":0,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"林鄭你條臭閪一味上北京䑛共<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9b86f16590f6a67bbd9eaf4eba12e3b0d4c4cf","tid":949030,"uid":103325,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"但特首就只會叫我地尊重其他國家法律"},{"pid":"3beb3e035271ea6592bf18d04db1e89d0aa43ca0","tid":949030,"uid":1