":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n【Consular staff reach out to BN(O) prisoners in the region 探訪區內英國國民（海外）在囚人士】<br />\n<br />\nConsular staff from the British Consulate-General in Hong Kong had recently visited British National (Overseas) prisoners in Thailand, Indonesia, the Philippines and Taiwan. Read more: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2R6nOox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R6nOox&d=qOnrDpP%2BJXSbynmDzAHLI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=60da7c6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2R6nOox</a><br />\n<br />\n英國駐香港總領事館領事部的同事，近日探訪了於泰國、印尼、菲律賓及台灣的英國國民（海外）在囚人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUKandHongKong%2F&d=qOnrDpP%2BJXSbynmDzAHLI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b9846dcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/image_data/file/82821/BNO_visit18-IMG-6839_960x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fimage_data%2Ffile%2F82821%2FBNO_visit18-IMG-6839_960x640.jpg&h=7323e6f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2dbe59c2dd08c04bfe52cc3675b3b257683d6c6","tid":949030,"uid":92301,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"英國駐港總領事館指出，作為英國政府對 BNO 持有人的一部分承諾，英國領事館工作人員將至少每年訪問或聯繫被拘留在海外監獄的 BNO 持有人。今年，英國駐香港總領事館的領事館工作人員，與英國駐泰國大使館、印尼和菲律賓的人員，以及台北的英國辦事處合作，安排聯合領事訪問。<br />\n<br />\n而這項聯合訪問，讓&nbsp;40 名持 BNO 囚犯，與會說廣東話的英國領事館官員會面，並討論任何令人關注的問題。英國總領事館的工作人員也可以傳遞香港家庭成員的訊息，並分發當地華文雜誌。領事館工作人員還可以利用他們的訪問來檢視囚犯的健康和福利，特別是在標準低於英國或香港拘留設施中的囚犯。<br />\n<br />\n四名港人早前被菲律賓法院判處藏毒罪成，判囚終身；協助他們的立法會議員涂謹申曾指，當地中國大使館人員探望次數較少，令四名港人感受到不到他們的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/英駐港總領館派操粵語官員-探望泰國菲律賓等服刑持-bno-港人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%8B%B1%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%B8%BD%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%B4%BE%E6%93%8D%E7%B2%B5%E8%AA%9E%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1-%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91%E6%8C%81-bno-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=qOnrDpP%2BJXSbynmDzAHLI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=dd6a758d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%8B%B1%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%B8%BD%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%B4%BE%E6%93%8D%E7%B2%B5%E8%AA%9E%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1-%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91%E6%8C%81-bno-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=03dbb05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/英駐港總領館派操粵語官員-探望泰國菲律賓等服刑持-bno-港人/</a>"},{"pid":"621843e00283948f795e37258fce74a4b4386b27","tid":949030,"uid":38795,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"fe9b86f16590f6a67bbd9eaf4eba12e3b0d4c4cf","tid":949030,"uid":103325,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"但特首就只會叫我地尊重其他國家法律"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"一邊自已人出左事即刻去探<br />\n另一邊自已人出左事唔關心不突止仲要幫對家踩多兩腳"},{"pid":"6282d2368b2af5bf085abc96e61a2c137c30564c","tid":949030,"uid":550,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"621843e00283948f795e37258fce74a4b4386b27","tid":949030,"uid":38795,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"fe9b86f16590f6a67bbd9eaf4eba12e3b0d4c4cf","tid":949030,"uid":103325,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"但特首就只會叫我地尊重其他國家法律"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"一邊自已人出左事即刻去探<br />\n另一邊自已人出左事唔關心不突止仲要幫對家踩多兩腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟三本護照即刻仆出嚟解畫添<img 